(1, 'Thanh Ton Mt Phn', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\"><u>K&iacute;nh gi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch</u>:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;\">Kinh gi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><u>K&iacute;nh gi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch</u>:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 11px;\">sadsdas</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\"><strong>Hp ng bo him s: [[$PRefNo]]&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">C&ocirc;ng ty Bo Him Nh&acirc;n Th Dai-ichi Vit Nam (&ldquo;Dai-ichi Life Vit Nam&rdquo;) xin gi n Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch li ch&agrave;o tr&acirc;n trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: jhttp://pacific.com/admin/letter_templateustify;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i xin th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o n Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kt qu xem x&eacute;t H s y&ecirc;u cu gii quyt Quyn li&nbsp;[[$benefitOfClaim]] ca Ngi c bo him <strong>[[$memberNameCap]]</strong> vi th&ocirc;ng tin:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">[[$IOPDiag]]&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">Cn c c&aacute;c iu khon &atilde; k&yacute; kt trong Hp ng, quyn li bo him c gii quyt nh sau:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;