(3, 'Tm Thi nh Ch', '<p>K&iacute;nh gi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch: &nbsp;[[$applicantName]]&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>C&ocirc;ng ty Bo him Nh&acirc;n th Dai-ichi Vit Nam (&ldquo;Dai-ichi Life Vit Nam&rdquo;) xin gi n Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch li ch&agrave;o tr&acirc;n trng.</p>\r\n<p>Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i rt tic phi th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o n Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vic tm &igrave;nh ch xem x&eacute;t H s y&ecirc;u cu gii quyt quyn li bo him li&ecirc;n quan n &nbsp;[[$IOPDiag]]&nbsp;.</p>\r\n<p>Do Dai-ichi Life Vit Nam cha nhn c chng t &atilde; n&ecirc;u trong c&aacute;c Th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o y&ecirc;u cu b sung h s &atilde; gi n Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch bao gm:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Chng t y t (S kh&aacute;m bnh, B&igrave;a s kh&aacute;m bnh, Phiu kh&aacute;m bnh, B&aacute;o c&aacute;o y t, Toa thuc&hellip;) c&oacute; th hin t&ecirc;n bnh nh&acirc;n l&agrave; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch, chn o&aacute;n bnh, c&oacute; ch k&yacute; v&agrave; t&ecirc;n B&aacute;c s iu tr </strong><strong>v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 20/07/2019, ng&agrave;y 21/07/2019, ng&agrave;y 22/07/2019, ng&agrave;y 23/07/2019, ng&agrave;y 24/07/2019, ng&agrave;y 25/07/2019, 26/07/2019 ti Ph&ograve;ng Kh&aacute;m a Khoa Phc Hi Chc Nng An Nhi&ecirc;n</strong><strong>.</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Chng t y t (S kh&aacute;m bnh, B&igrave;a s kh&aacute;m bnh, Phiu kh&aacute;m bnh, B&aacute;o c&aacute;o y t, Toa thuc&hellip;) c&oacute; th hin t&ecirc;n bnh nh&acirc;n l&agrave; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch, chn o&aacute;n bnh, c&oacute; ch k&yacute; v&agrave; t&ecirc;n B&aacute;c s iu tr </strong><strong>v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 22/07/2019 ti Bnh Vin Th&acirc;n D&acirc;n.</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Chng t y t (S kh&aacute;m bnh, B&igrave;a s kh&aacute;m bnh, Phiu kh&aacute;m bnh, B&aacute;o c&aacute;o y t, Toa thuc&hellip;) c&oacute; th hin t&ecirc;n bnh nh&acirc;n l&agrave; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch, chn o&aacute;n bnh, c&oacute; ch k&yacute; v&agrave; t&ecirc;n B&aacute;c s iu tr</strong><strong> v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 30/07/201